 ( array count function -- )
 {
   variable| array fn |
   [ i 1- array @ ] is I
   [ fn ! swap array ! [ I array.get fn @ invoke I array.put ] +iterate ]
 } is map-array
 
 ( Build an array )
 5 cells is-array a
 10 0 a array.put
 11 1 a array.put
 12 2 a array.put
 13 3 a array.put
 14 4 a array.put
 
 ( Add 1 to each item in the array )
 a 5 ` 1+ map-array
